title: FS: T205 George Gibson - American Beauty Back SOLD
author: quinnsryche

posts.post_title: FS: T205 George Gibson - American Beauty Back SOLD
posts.post_content:
Ok guys, since I have absolutely no experience with back rarity on t205's, I am going to rely on the honor system here. I have 1 T205 available that came in a collection of 50's-70's cards. It's a George Gibson that looks to be in excellent condition (about a PSA 4 in my assumption). Scans are attached below. I don't know if this is a $50 card or a $500 card or somewhere in between. If someone wants to give me a ballpark figure on what to ask publicly I would appreciate it or I can just accept an offer that sounds reasonable. Please just be fair and honest as I'm sure some will chime in with lowball offers and some will be respectable.
Thanks for looking and good luck!
Tony

NOW SOLD - THANKS MICHAEL!
